@@yNinth Descent@@W                                        Sentinel level 35

Syntax: ninth descent

Enter the focused perceptive state of the silence-court descent ritual.
For 4 combat rounds, each successful avoidance (dodge, parry, or block)
grants +2 testimony instead of +1. Measured Response procs during Ninth
Descent also grant +2.

@@yDetails:@@W
  * Mana cost: 25 (roughly 25% of pool at level 35).
  * Cooldown: 20 rounds.
  * Can only be used while fighting.
  * This is the Sentinel's burst window — pop it, survive 4 rounds of
    incoming attacks, and reach high verdict tiers in half the time.

Named for the Khenari Doctrine of Ninth Descent — the nine-stage chant
structure of the silence-court ritual where each descent deepened perceptive
acuity.

See also: @@mtestimony verdict sentinel@@W
